title: How Family Guy Changed Meg Griffin Forever

media:group.media:title: How Family Guy Changed Meg Griffin Forever
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the entire evolution of Meg Griffin from Family Guy. Voiced by Mila Kunis, we look at Meg's entire life history, her past and future. Taking a look at the Family Guy cutaways, as well as the full Family Guy episodes, I've put Meg's life in chronological order. From season 1 to newest Family Guy season.

We also look at the funniest Family Guy moments from Peter, Lois, Chris, Meg and Brian. As well as other Family Guy characters from Quahog Rhode Island.
